HEADWORD: mapping
<hw>map"ping</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>A function such
that for every element of one set there is a unique element of another
set. Same as <er>map</er>{4}.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> map, correspondence.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

